|BKBStone Dwarves are a society of surface dwarves who long ago dedicated their
lives to working in the underworld in the service of Mitra. Like most
dwarves, they are short and stout and can hold their liquor, but Stone
Dwarves also have a high degree of goodness and lawfulness ingrained into
them at an early age. Their small size makes it difficult for them to wield
larger weapons, and working in cramped mines have a detrimental effect on
their joints, limiting their agility.

